description: Its pudding time boys. Yes thats right, I said pudding. These boys really know how to have a circle jerk, with a nice kiddie pool full of chocolate pudding. Everyone knows that before any circle jerk you must have a pudding wrestling contest to see how is the strongest and dirtiest guy. I really feel sorry for the owner of the dorm room. That pudding got everywhere, and when I say everywhere I mean EVERYWHERE.
title: What People Do
